268
00:17:38,683 --> 00:17:40,943
<i>And there's a lot more freedom,</i>
<i>I would say,</i>

269
00:17:41,018 --> 00:17:43,348
<i>because many lyrics are already poetry.</i>

270
00:17:43,437 --> 00:17:46,937
<i>So I guess I'm designing for poetry</i>
<i>to happen in, more often than prose.</i>

271
00:17:48,734 --> 00:17:52,914
<i>I really quite methodically go,</i>
<i>"Okay, let's listen to the lyrics,</i>

272
00:17:52,989 --> 00:17:55,659
<i>let's write down the lyrics</i>
